{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"printing press (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that around 1473 a Dominican friar denounced the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Printing_press\" title=\"Printing press\">printing press</a></b> <i>(example pictured)</i> as a \"whore\" set against the \"virgin\" pen?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Printing_press","retrieved":1782727701127},{"title":"an Australian newspaper (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/About_Time_(newspaper)\" title=\"About Time (newspaper)\">an Australian newspaper</a></b> is mainly written by people who are or have been in prison?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/About_Time_(newspaper)","retrieved":1782727701171},{"title":"who was murdered at the age of 27 (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that an endowed scholarship was established at Thomas Jefferson University in memory of transgender activist and fashion designer Dominique \"Rem'mie\" Fells, <b><a href=\"/wiki/Murder_of_Dominique_%22Rem%27mie%22_Fells\" title=\"Murder of Dominique &quot;Rem'mie&quot; Fells\">who was murdered at the age of 27</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Murder_of_Dominique_%22Rem%27mie%22_Fells","retrieved":1782727701171},{"title":"Notharctus (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Notharctus\" title=\"Notharctus\">Notharctus</a></b></i>, one of the first fossil primates discovered in the Americas, was originally classified as a <a href=\"/wiki/Pachydermata\" title=\"Pachydermata\">pachyderm</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Notharctus","retrieved":1782727701172},{"title":"Daz Black (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that many people attributed Andrew Tate's removal from social media to a diatribe by <b><a href=\"/wiki/Daz_Black\" title=\"Daz Black\">Daz Black</a></b>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daz_Black","retrieved":1782727701172},{"title":"